### ===== IMAGE PROCESSING =====

### Remove Background (Local)
# Removes background from an uploaded image
# Returns the image with transparent background in PNG format
#
# Request: Multipart form data with 'file' field
# Response: Image file (image/png)
POST {{localUrl}}/v1/image-processing/remove-bg
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test_image.jpg
--boundary--

### Remove Background (Production)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/image-processing/remove-bg
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test_image.jpg
--boundary--

### Remove Background via URL (Local)
# Removes background from an image URL
POST {{localUrl}}/v1/image-processing/remove-bg
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

image_url=https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/bearded-man-denim-shirt-round-glasses_273609-11768.jpg?t=st=1769486744~exp=1769490344~hmac=a50d5e064bf827ffd4d75e0bc557cd5bac427c6c2e25815148130ec18c4fca49&w=2000

### Remove Background via URL (Production)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/image-processing/remove-bg
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

image_url=https://img.freepik.com/premium-photo/man-with-beard-blue-shirt-is-standing-front-crowd_1187092-137326.jpg?w=2000

